                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "interaction",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Although Alisendra is on her own, the ambient energies of the Bastardhall Curse bolster her as if she were a part of a coven. She adds @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Nightmare], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Outcast's Curse], and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Scrying] to her innate spells.</p>"
